                    "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                },
                "html": "Elves crafted the original doorwardens in honor of their goddess of portals, <a aonid=\"30\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Alseta</a>. Such doorwardens (such as the one in this volume's adventure) are similar to the one presented here, but they speak Elven instead of Common, wield specially crafted elven curve blades rather than longswords, and may have great knowledge of elven culture and religion."
            }
